211
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:54,350
Code name... "Laugh out loud, Manager Seong!

212
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:56,120
Laugh out loud, Gaboss!"

213
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:58,220
Hey, listen to yourselves.

214
00:11:58,220 --> 00:11:59,950
