231
00:12:41,670 --> 00:12:42,960
The moment I see that car, I'd say—

232
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:46,100
Cha Wa-Wa.
(Cha=car, Wa-Wa=Whoa, Whoa in Korean)

233
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:49,590
